PLACEHOLDER FILE (text)

This repository does not ship a binary photo by default.
Replace this file with a real `.webp` image before publishing docs.

How to source a CC-licensed laptop photo:

1) Go to Wikimedia Commons media search:
   https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:MediaSearch?type=image&search=laptop%20computer
2) Open an image with license marked CC0, CC BY, or CC BY-SA.
3) Download a web-sized version and convert to `.webp`:
   `magick source.jpg -quality 85 assets/laptop.webp`
4) Add attribution in `README.md`:
   - Photo title
   - Author
   - License
   - Source URL

